Package: HEMDAG
Title: Hierarchical Ensemble Methods for Directed Acyclic Graphs
Version: 2.3.6
Author: Marco Notaro [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4309-2200>),
  Alessandro Petrini [ctb] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-0587-1484>),
